      <procstep>
        <procdesc>The dataset was copied from the CD obtained from Washington, DC 2005

The landmarks were identified from public records (including published maps and a database from National Capital Planning Commission) and polygons extracted from the digital version of the National Park Service Map A. They were digitized from 1995 orthophotos, converted to polygons, and corrected to the planimetric building footprints. Attribute data was provided by public records.

All DC GIS data is stored and exported in Maryland State Plane coordinates NAD 83 meters.</procdesc>
